00:22:01.870 --> 00:22:03.453 align:middle line:84%
Half the patients,
they gave the drug.

00:22:03.453 --> 00:22:05.920 align:middle line:84%
Half the patients, they
gave a placebo, a fake.

00:22:05.920 --> 00:22:08.045 align:middle line:84%
No one knew who was receiving
the real drug or not.

00:22:08.045 --> 00:22:10.295 align:middle line:84%
