really bad for me, that I'm--

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:25.340 align:middle line:84%
I may be responding to
the model of reality

00:22:25.340 --> 00:22:30.460 align:middle line:84%
more than the nutritional
aspects of the donut.

00:22:30.460 --> 00:22:33.790 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think the stories
of this kind have been known

00:22:33.790 --> 00:22:36.472 align:middle line:84%
