00:23:08.870 --> 00:23:09.670 align:middle line:90%
>> That's true.

00:23:09.670 --> 00:23:11.840 align:middle line:84%
And it also can be
applied in another way.

00:23:11.840 --> 00:23:15.410 align:middle line:10%
